vernac_cmds: Lemma group_inverse_inj : forall (G : GROUP) (g g' : G), Equal (group_inverse _ g) (group_inverse _ g') -> Equal g g'.
apply Trans with (group_inverse _ (group_inverse _ g)); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (sgroup_law _ (group_inverse _ g') g'); auto with algebra.
Lemma subtype_elt_comp : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A) (b b' : B), Equal b b' -> Equal (subtype_elt b) (subtype_elt b').
Lemma subtype_elt_inj : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A) (b b' : B), Equal (subtype_elt b) (subtype_elt b') -> Equal b b'.
Lemma in_part_subtype_elt : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A) (b : B), in_part (subtype_elt b) B.
Definition inject_subsets : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A), part_set B -> part_set A.
apply (Build_Predicate (Pred_fun:=fun a : A => exists c : C, Equal a (subtype_elt (subtype_elt c)))).
generalize dependent x0; intro c; intros.
apply Trans with x; auto with algebra.
Lemma inject_subsets_comp : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A) (C C' : part_set B), Equal C C' -> Equal (inject_subsets C) (inject_subsets C').
generalize (H1 H3); clear H1 H2 H3; intro.
generalize (H2 H3); clear H1 H2 H3; intro.
Lemma inject_subsets_of_part_set_included : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A) (C : part_set B), included (inject_subsets C) B.
apply in_part_comp_l with (subtype_elt (subtype_elt x0)); auto with algebra.
Lemma inject_subsets_full_inv : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A), Equal (inject_subsets (full B)) B.
generalize dependent subtype_elt; intro b; intros.
apply in_part_comp_l with (subtype_elt b); auto with algebra.
assert (in_part b (full B)); simpl in |- *; auto.
Definition inject_subsetsify : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A) (C : part_set B), C -> inject_subsets C.
assert (exists c : C, Equal c' (subtype_elt (subtype_elt c))).
Lemma inject_subsetsify_comp : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A) (C : part_set B) (c c' : C), Equal c c' -> Equal (inject_subsetsify c) (inject_subsetsify c').
Definition uninject_subsetsify : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A) (C : part_set B), inject_subsets C -> C.
apply in_part_comp_l with (subtype_elt (subtype_elt x)); auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_l with (subtype_elt x); auto with algebra.
Lemma uninject_subsetsify_comp : forall (A : Setoid) (B : part_set A) (C : part_set B), fun_compatible (uninject_subsetsify (A:=A) (B:=B) (C:=C)).
Lemma in_part_included : forall (A : Setoid) (B C : part_set A) (a : A), in_part a B -> included B C -> in_part a C.
Lemma exists_difference : forall n m : nat, n <= m -> exists q : nat, m = n + q.
generalize (IHm H0); intro p; inversion_clear p.
